WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:03.566
What are you looking for me for?

2
00:00:03.666 --> 00:00:05.200
It's nothing, I'll go first

3
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.800
Waste time don't go

4
00:00:12.466 --> 00:00:15.266
Brother Xiaoyu has decided to divorce you

5
00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:18.433
Why didn't you hear it clearly?

6
00:00:18.533 --> 00:00:20.500
I'll say it again if I don't hear you

7
00:00:20.566 --> 00:00:23.666
Brother Xiaoyu has decided to divorce you

8
00:00:23.666 --> 00:00:25.466
What nonsense is Lianyue talking about?

9
00:00:26.533 --> 00:00:27.333
Xu Zeyu

10
00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.166
Why did you divorce me?

11
00:00:29.166 --> 00:00:30.300
So many years

12
00:00:30.466 --> 00:00:32.900
I worked so hard outside to support this family

13
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:35.900
I do all the big and small things at home

14
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.700
I was so nice to you, why did you divorce me?

15
00:00:39.100 --> 00:00:40.666
Shut your mouth for me, okay?

16
00:00:41.566 --> 00:00:43.466
Why can't I divorce you?

17
00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:45.466
You have worked hard for so many years

18
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:47.400
Am I not working hard for this family?

19
00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:48.766
Steamed buns I tell you

20
00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:51.033
Don't think that you are the only one working hard

21
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:52.666
I work harder than you

22
00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:54.966
I have been living in your shadow

23
00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:57.566
I have to settle accounts for everything I do

24
00:00:57.866 --> 00:00:58.900
Any quarrel

25
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.200
Right or wrong

26
00:01:00.533 --> 00:01:01.866
I apologize first

27
00:01:02.133 --> 00:01:03.200
I tell you An Tong

28
00:01:04.900 --> 00:01:06.766
I've had enough of this life

29
00:01:07.766 --> 00:01:08.666
Xu Zeyu

30
00:01:09.866 --> 00:01:12.200
Didn't you say

31
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.833
Whether I live or die has nothing to do with you

32
00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:17.933
If I wasn't still useful

33
00:01:17.933 --> 00:01:19.266
You would have kicked me out long ago

34
00:01:19.266 --> 00:01:20.600
Fall into Yang Yijie's arms, don't you?

35
00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:22.266
I didn't mean that.

36
00:01:23.933 --> 00:01:25.233
Yes, yes, Li Yue

37
00:01:25.566 --> 00:01:26.800
It's Li Yueta

38
00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:29.400
Cut it out.

39
00:01:29.933 --> 00:01:31.233
Sign it

40
00:01:32.666 --> 00:01:33.500
Let's go

